Description of Webapp

 1. Technology Used - React and Firebase
 2. Firebase is used for the Realtime database communication
 3. User can directly send the message by entering their name
 4. It store the User Information in the Firebase in JSON Format

Deployment Instructions 

 1. Directly Fetch the GitHub Repository from the link Also create the firebase config object by creating the project in firebase
 2. After fetching the link use the firebase object in the firebase.js and put the folder on your GitHub repository 
 3.  Open the Folder in Terminal use the Command `npm i` this will install all the packages that needed
 4. use the `npm start` to run on the local server
 5. Use the Heroku to fetch the repository from you GitHub account and use the buil
